%20%20%20%20%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%22160%22%20width%3D%22160%22%20x%3D%22890%22%20y%3D%2254.5%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%20%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2FmxCell%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxCell%20id%3D%22v73PD94NMpmLlStmtWzA-4%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22text%3Bhtml%3D1%3BwhiteSpace%3Dwrap%3BstrokeColor%3Dnone%3BfillColor%3Dnone%3Balign%3Dleft%3BverticalAlign%3Dmiddle%3Brounded%3D0%3B%22%20value%3D%22Attempt%20%231%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%2230%22%20width%3D%2270%22%20x%3D%22440%22%20y%3D%2240%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%20%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2FmxCell%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxCell%20id%3D%22v73PD94NMpmLlStmtWzA-16%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22rounded%3D0%3Balign%3Dleft%3BwhiteSpace%3Dwrap%3BfontSize%3D10%3B%22%20value%3D%22%23%23%23%20Step-by-Step%20Reasoning%26%23xa%3BIn%20the%20past%20attempt%2C%20the%20player%20revealed%20cells%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20and%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\).%20The%20resulting%20state%20showed%20that%20row%206%2C%20column%201%20is%20a%201%2C%20row%206%2C%20column%202%20is%20a%20%3F%2C%20row%206%2C%20column%203%20is%20a%20*%2C%20and%20row%206%2C%20column%204%20is%20a%20%3F.%20This%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20a%20mine%20at%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20game%20ended%20in%20a%20loss.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3B%23%23%23%23%20Mistakes%20and%20Inefficiencies%3A%26%23xa%3B1.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)**%3A%20This%20revealed%20a%201%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20exactly%20one%20mine%20in%20the%208%20neighboring%20cells.%20However%2C%20since%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20is%20adjacent%20to%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\)%20and%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)%2C%20this%20information%20is%20limited%20and%20not%20very%20helpful%20in%20identifying%20the%20exact%20location%20of%20the%20mine.%26%23xa%3B2.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)**%3A%20This%20revealed%20a%20*%2C%20indicating%20that%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%20is%20a%20mine.%20This%20is%20a%20direct%20loss%2C%20but%20it%20also%20provides%20some%20information%20about%20the%20surrounding%20cells.%26%23xa%3B3.%20**Lack%20of%20strategic%20focus**%3A%20The%20player%20did%20not%20consider%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20numbers%20in%20row%204%20and%20row%205%2C%20which%20are%201s%20and%202s%2C%20suggesting%20that%20there%20are%20nearby%20mines.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3B%23%23%23%20New%20Plan%20of%20Action%26%23xa%3BTo%20improve%20the%20strategy%2C%20the%20player%20should%20focus%20on%20revealing%20cells%20that%20provide%20the%20most%20information%20without%20risking%20a%20direct%20reveal%20of%20a%20mine.%20Here%26%2339%3Bs%20a%20revised%20plan%3A%26%23xa%3B1.%20**Reveal%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20and%20\\\(4%2C%201\\\).%20Revealing%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)%20would%20help%20determine%20if%20there%20is%20a%20mine%20nearby%2C%20especially%20since%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20is%20a%201%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20exactly%20one%20mine%20in%20the%208%20neighboring%20cells.%26%23xa%3B2.%20**Reveal%20\\\(5%2C%202\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\)%20and%20\\\(4%2C%202\\\).%20It%20would%20help%20determine%20if%20there%20is%20a%20mine%20near%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%3F.%26%23xa%3B3.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%20\\\(which%20is%20a%20mine\\\)%20and%20\\\(5%2C%204\\\).%20Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)%20would%20help%20determine%20if%20there%20is%20a%20mine%20nearby%2C%20especially%20since%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%20is%20a%20mine.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3B%23%23%23%20Reflection%20and%20Improved%20Plan%26%23xa%3B%26lt%3Bremark%26gt%3B%26%23xa%3BIn%20the%20past%20attempt%2C%20revealing%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20and%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%20led%20to%20a%20loss%20because%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%20was%20a%20mine.%20To%20avoid%20this%2C%20the%20next%20step%20should%20be%20to%20reveal%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)%20to%20check%20the%20surrounding%20cells%20without%20directly%20revealing%20a%20mine.%20After%20that%2C%20revealing%20\\\(5%2C%202\\\)%20would%20help%20determine%20if%20there%20is%20a%20mine%20near%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\).%20Finally%2C%20revealing%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)%20would%20help%20identify%20any%20nearby%20mines%20adjacent%20to%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\).%20This%20approach%20would%20provide%20more%20information%20without%20risking%20a%20direct%20hit%20on%20a%20mine.%26%23xa%3B%26lt%3B%2Fremark%26gt%3B%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%22330%22%20width%3D%22675%22%20x%3D%22425%22%20y%3D%22229%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%20%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2FmxCell%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxCell%20id%3D%22v73PD94NMpmLlStmtWzA-19%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22text%3BwhiteSpace%3Dwrap%3BstrokeColor%3Ddefault%3BfontSize%3D10%3B%22%20value%3D%22%23%23%23%20Step-by-Step%20Reasoning%26%23xa%3BIn%20the%20past%20attempt%2C%20the%20player%20revealed%20the%20cells%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%206\\\)%2C%20and%20\\\(6%2C%205\\\).%20The%20resulting%20state%20showed%20some%20progress%2C%20but%20the%20task%20was%20not%20completed%20successfully.%20Let%26%2339%3Bs%20analyze%20what%20went%20wrong%3A%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3B1.%20**Revealing%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%204%2C%20which%20has%20three%201s.%20Revealing%20\\\(5%2C%201\\\)%20would%20have%20revealed%20the%20surrounding%20cells%2C%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%201%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%20However%2C%20this%20didn%26%2339%3Bt%20provide%20enough%20information%20to%20determine%20the%20exact%20location%20of%20the%20mines.%26%23xa%3B2.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%204%2C%20which%20is%20a%202.%20Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)%20would%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20of%20mines%20around%20it%2C%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%201%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B3.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%201%2C%20which%20is%20a%201.%20Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%20would%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20of%20mines%20around%20it%2C%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%201%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B4.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%206\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%206%2C%20which%20is%20a%201.%20Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%206\\\)%20would%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20of%20mines%20around%20it%2C%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%201%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B5.%20**Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%205\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%205%2C%20which%20is%20a%201.%20Revealing%20\\\(6%2C%205\\\)%20would%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20of%20mines%20around%20it%2C%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%201%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3BThe%20main%20issue%20was%20that%20the%20player%20did%20not%20focus%20on%20revealing%20cells%20that%20would%20provide%20more%20direct%20information%20about%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mines.%20Instead%2C%20the%20player%20revealed%20cells%20that%20were%20adjacent%20to%20already%20revealed%20cells%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20unnecessary%20information%20and%20not%20enough%20progress%20toward%20identifying%20the%20exact%20location%20of%20the%20mines.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3B%23%23%23%20New%20Plan%20of%20Action%26%23xa%3BTo%20improve%20the%20strategy%2C%20the%20player%20should%20focus%20on%20revealing%20cells%20that%20are%20not%20adjacent%20to%20already%20revealed%20cells%2C%20and%20that%20are%20far%20enough%20away%20to%20avoid%20being%20affected%20by%20the%20auto-cascade%20effect.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20identify%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mines%20by%20revealing%20cells%20that%20are%20not%20adjacent%20to%20any%20already%20revealed%20cells%2C%20and%20that%20are%20in%20areas%20where%20the%20numbers%20indicate%20a%20higher%20likelihood%20of%20a%20mine.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3BHere%20is%20a%20revised%20plan%3A%26%23xa%3B1.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20not%20adjacent%20to%20any%20already%20revealed%20cells%20and%20is%20far%20enough%20away%20to%20avoid%20being%20affected%20by%20the%20auto-cascade%20effect.%20It%20is%20also%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%202%2C%20which%20is%20a%202%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B2.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20not%20adjacent%20to%20any%20already%20revealed%20cells%20and%20is%20far%20enough%20away%20to%20avoid%20being%20affected%20by%20the%20auto-cascade%20effect.%20It%20is%20also%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%203%2C%20which%20is%20a%202%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%26%23xa%3B3.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%201%2C%20which%20is%20a%201%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%20However%2C%20since%20it%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%206%2C%20column%202%2C%20which%20is%20a%201%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20reveal%20this%20cell%20to%20confirm%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mine.%26%23xa%3B4.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%204%2C%20which%20is%20a%202%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%20However%2C%20since%20it%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%206%2C%20column%203%2C%20which%20is%20a%201%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20reveal%20this%20cell%20to%20confirm%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mine.%26%23xa%3B5.%20**Reveal%20\\\(6%2C%205\\\)**%3A%20This%20cell%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%205%2C%20column%205%2C%20which%20is%20a%201%2C%20indicating%20that%20there%20is%20at%20least%20one%20mine%20nearby.%20However%2C%20since%20it%20is%20adjacent%20to%20row%206%2C%20column%204%2C%20which%20is%20a%201%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20reveal%20this%20cell%20to%20confirm%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mine.%26%23xa%3B%26%23xa%3BBy%20following%20this%20plan%2C%20the%20player%20can%20identify%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mines%20more%20effectively%20and%20avoid%20the%20mistakes%20made%20in%20the%20previous%20attempt.%26%23xa%3B%26lt%3Bremark%26gt%3B%26%23xa%3BIn%20the%20past%20attempt%2C%20the%20player%20revealed%20cells%20that%20were%20adjacent%20to%20already%20revealed%20cells%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20unnecessary%20information%20and%20not%20enough%20progress%20toward%20identifying%20the%20exact%20location%20of%20the%20mines.%20To%20improve%20the%20strategy%2C%20the%20player%20should%20focus%20on%20revealing%20cells%20that%20are%20not%20adjacent%20to%20any%20already%20revealed%20cells%2C%20and%20that%20are%20far%20enough%20away%20to%20avoid%20being%20affected%20by%20the%20auto-cascade%20effect.%20The%20revised%20plan%20involves%20revealing%20cells%20such%20as%20\\\(6%2C%202\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%203\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%201\\\)%2C%20\\\(6%2C%204\\\)%2C%20and%20\\\(6%2C%205\\\)%20to%20identify%20the%20location%20of%20the%20mines%20more%20effectively.%26%23xa%3B%26lt%3B%2Fremark%26gt%3B%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%22530%22%20width%3D%22675%22%20x%3D%22425%22%20y%3D%22580%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%20%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2FmxCell%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxCell%20id%3D%22v73PD94NMpmLlStmtWzA-20%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22text%3Bhtml%3D1%3BwhiteSpace%3Dwrap%3BstrokeColor%3Dnone%3BfillColor%3Dnone%3Balign%3Dleft%3BverticalAlign%3Dmiddle%3Brounded%3D0%3B%22%20value%3D%22Reflection%20%231%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%2230%22%20width%3D%2290%22%20x%3D%22345%22%20y%3D%22229%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%20%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C